text: Knut Håkon Tangen (21 May 1928 – 2 April 2007 in Hurdalssjøen) is a Norwegian speed skater. He competed at the 1956 Winter Olympics, where he placed 19th in the 10,000 metre. ==References== == External links == * Category:1928 births Category:2007 deaths Category:Norwegian male speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of Norway Category:Speed skaters at the 1956 Winter Olympics
